# game/day 14.rpy:20
translate chinese_simplified day14_0e7325ed:

    # "Ah,{w=.3} the Bon Festival will be here soon.{p}My stay at Minasato Village is about half over."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "啊，{w=.3}盂兰盆节快到了。{p}我在水乡村的停留已经过了一半了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:21
translate chinese_simplified day14_a6aa2e82:

    # "But there have been a few things in the\nfirst half of the month since I got here."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "不过，自从来到这里之后，在这半个月里也发生了不少事情。"

# game/day 14.rpy:22
translate chinese_simplified day14_7f854626:

    # "First there was the welcoming party.\nAfter that, we split up again, but then everybody\nwent to the beach and had a good time."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "首先是欢迎会。{p}在那之后，我们又分开了，但之后大家一起去海边玩得很开心。"

# game/day 14.rpy:23
translate chinese_simplified day14_a34799f0:

    # "That was fun, I'd like to go on another trip with\neverybody."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "那次真开心，真想再和大家一起去旅行。"

# game/day 14.rpy:24
translate chinese_simplified day14_f4f62d4d:

    # "They'll probably be busy by the end of the\nmonth, though, so I better take action ahead of time."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "不过，月底大家可能都会忙起来，{p}所以我还是提前行动比较好。"

# game/day 14.rpy:25
translate chinese_simplified day14_ac7877d9:

    # "That's right!{p}This time I should be the one to invite everybody."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "没错！{p}这次应该由我来邀请大家。"

# game/day 14.rpy:26
translate chinese_simplified day14_ca63dfab:

    # "It seems like they have a contact network,\nso I'll try calling somebody."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "他们好像有联络网，{p}我先试着打电话给谁吧。"

# game/day 14.rpy:27
translate chinese_simplified day14_7f771330:

    # "However, if I'm planning it,\nI'll have to set everything up.{p}Maybe I should search for something to do first."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "不过，既然是我来计划，{p}就必须把所有事情安排好。{p}也许我该先找找有什么可做的。"

# game/day 14.rpy:28
translate chinese_simplified day14_391dd29c:

    # "What day would be convenient for everybody?{p}Hmm, maybe I should call them first.{p}After that..."
    # [机翻] 来源: deepseek-v4-flash
    "大家哪天方便呢？{p}嗯，也许我该先打电话给他们。{p}然后再……"

# game/day 14.rpy:43
translate chinese_simplified day14_47201822:

    # fn "「Awawawawawa, this is bad.{p} This is...{w=.3} really bad.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 14-15)
    fn "「呜哇哇哇哇哇，糟了。{p} 太糟糕了，{w=.3}糟糕透了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:44
translate chinese_simplified day14_5acbfd5f:

    # "Why do I have to sprint as\nfast as I can this morning..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 17)
    "为什么[fn]一大早就得这样全力奔跑呢……{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:45
translate chinese_simplified day14_ff3c435a:

    # "That's right, this is all my fault.{p}Why could it only be today."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 18-19)
    "啊啊对了，都是[fn]的错。{p} 为什么偏偏就今天会这样呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:49
translate chinese_simplified day14_2007093e:

    # "Ah, there they are."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 22)
    "啊，看见他们了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:61
translate chinese_simplified day14_f4c96389:

    # su "「Ahh,{w=.3} [fn]-san, you're late.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 34)
    su "「啊～{w=.3}[fn]哥，你迟到了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:62
translate chinese_simplified day14_928698ee:

    # "I meet Shun-kun at the park,\nhis swishing tail greeting me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 36-37)
    "当[fn]到达大家集合的公园时， 峻摇着尾巴出来迎接了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:63
translate chinese_simplified day14_7f82f05e:

    # to "「Oh,{w=.3} you finally showed up.{p} I was getting tired of waiting.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 40-41)
    to "「喔！{w=.3}主办方总算来了啊。{p} 等的都快累死了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:64
translate chinese_simplified day14_0ce8d45d:

    # ju "「[ln], it's unusual for you\n to be late on a day like today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 44)
    ju "「[ln]在这种日子里会迟到什么的，还真少见呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:65
translate chinese_simplified day14_00c3a2e2:

    # si "「Are you not the one who organised this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 47)
    si "「是因为还没习惯做这种事吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:66
translate chinese_simplified day14_d91bdc2c:

    # "Just as I expected, everybody's already here.{p}I talked to them all on the phone, but..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 49)
    "果然大家都已经到了。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:67
translate chinese_simplified day14_0923876d:

    # "I never would have thought that we\nwere going to go the very next day..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 50-51)
    "[fn]开始打电话后，事情的进展就越谈越顺利。{w=.3} 根本没想到突然决定在第二天就出发……"

# game/day 14.rpy:68
translate chinese_simplified day14_0bf6b317:

    # fn "「Sorry, I overslept.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 54)
    fn "「抱歉，[fn]起晚了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:79
translate chinese_simplified day14_046e18ee:

    # ko "「You weren't prepared to get up early?{p} That's not good if you're not staying alert\n on a day like this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 67-68)
    ko "「因为觉得自己能早起就大意了是吧？{p} 不行哦，像今天这样的日子行动起来就得利利索索地」"

# game/day 14.rpy:83
translate chinese_simplified day14_8f2cd130:

    # ka "「Wait,{w=.3} you shouldn't be the one saying that...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 72)
    ka "「等下，{w=.3}你可没资格说别人呀……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:84
translate chinese_simplified day14_70a79127:

    # fn "「That's right,{w=.3} you have no right to talk.{p} I should be the one saying something about\n you getting here on time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 75-76)
    fn "「就是，{w=.3}[fn]可不想被孝之助这么说呢。{p} 既然你会这么说，那就表示你有准时来集合吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:88
translate chinese_simplified day14_d3f289f5:

    # ko "「That's very true.{p} I did get here earlier than usual today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 80-81)
    ko "「那是当然的。{p} 我今天可是比平时要早来很多呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:93
translate chinese_simplified day14_6764d4d4:

    # fn "{size=+15}「THAT'S A LIE!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 86)
    fn "「说谎！！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:94
translate chinese_simplified day14_beed9c20:

    # ky "「...In order to get here ahead of time,\n you would have to slow down time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 89)
    ky "「……确实是比平时早了，但还是比集合的时间晚」"

# game/day 14.rpy:95
translate chinese_simplified day14_244efff6:

    # fn "「That's being late isn't it!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 92)
    fn "「结果还不是迟到嘛！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:99
translate chinese_simplified day14_f304cfea:

    # ko "「I was a little late, but there's\n no reason to complain.{w} The important thing\n is that I got here earlier, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 96-97)
    ko "「就迟那么一点点而已就别在这斤斤计较啦。{p} 比起这个，『我早来了』这点才最重要吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:100
translate chinese_simplified day14_e8a06c38:

    # fn "「That's still the same as being late...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 100)
    fn "「迟到了的话，不就跟平时一样嘛……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:111
translate chinese_simplified day14_e9663ff5:

    # to "「What's strange about that?{p} Who was it that was late when he finally got here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 113-114)
    to "「诶，很奇怪不是吗？{p} 最晚来的家伙，到底是谁呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:112
translate chinese_simplified day14_7bef3ccc:

    # fn "「Well... that's-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 117)
    fn "「啊呀……那是……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:116
translate chinese_simplified day14_78d8d3a9:

    # si "「Even though you're about to say something,\n I want you to be level-headed.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 121-122)
    si "「既然这是你提出来的，希望你能认真对待呢。{p} 那么你想怎么来负起这个责任呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:118
translate chinese_simplified day14_347dd13c:

    # extend "How are you going to take responsibility for this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 125)
    extend "既然被深说了要负责任了……"

# game/day 14.rpy:119
translate chinese_simplified day14_d4a1c9f5:

    # "Aah, Shin-kun, don't look at me like that.{p}How would I take responsibility for this?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 124)
    "啊啊，深，别用那种眼神看着我。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:120
translate chinese_simplified day14_dfc37587:

    # to "「I know how you'll take responsibility.{p} A punishment game.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 128)
    to "「就是，要负责任哦。惩罚游戏喔」"

# game/day 14.rpy:121
translate chinese_simplified day14_418da165:

    # fn "「But why only me this time?{p} Isn't this bullying?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 131-132)
    fn "「为什么就[fn]迟到的时候要这样啊。{p} 这不等于在欺负[fn]嘛」"

# game/day 14.rpy:125
translate chinese_simplified day14_04ae75e1:

    # su "「What will the punishment game be?{p} I feel sorry for [fn]-san.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 136-137)
    su "「要玩惩罚游戏吗？{p} [fn]哥太可怜了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:126
translate chinese_simplified day14_8f0e194e:

    # "Shun-kun... you're so kind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 139)
    "峻……为什么你就这么善良呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:130
translate chinese_simplified day14_57ea38de:

    # ju "「It's okay, Kodori.{p} It will be something everybody can\n enjoy, so don't worry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 143-144)
    ju "「没关系的古酉。{p} 只是做让大家都会很高兴的事而已，不用担心」"

# game/day 14.rpy:131
translate chinese_simplified day14_90a01c1f:

    # su "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 147)
    su "「这样啊」"

# game/day 14.rpy:132
translate chinese_simplified day14_6c36e71f:

    # ju "「It will certainly also meet [ln]'s\n expectations.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 150)
    ju "「我想[ln]也一定能像大家的期待的那样的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:137
translate chinese_simplified day14_2a47761b:

    # su "「Okay, I undertand.{p} Please do your best, [fn]-san.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 154-155)
    su "「嗯，我明白了。{p} 要加油哦[fn]哥」"

# game/day 14.rpy:138
translate chinese_simplified day14_68d783e1:

    # "Shun-kun was easily convinced.{p}He's even backing them up with a smiling face..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 159)
    "峻这么简单就信服了啊。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:139
translate chinese_simplified day14_6d5eab0d:

    # "I should be more concerned about why\nJuuichi-san is so interested."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 162)
    "话说为什么柔一也这么起劲啊。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:140
translate chinese_simplified day14_5f5475c1:

    # "He's usually the one who puts a stop to this.{p}Oh, I see..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 162-163)
    "话说为什么柔一也这么起劲啊。{p} 平时都应该会帮忙阻止的。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:141
translate chinese_simplified day14_3f96052e:

    # fn "「Is that the kind of thing Juuichi-san is\n expecting of me?{p} Then I'll do my best for him!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 167-168)
    fn "「那意思是说柔一正期待[fn]吗？{p} 那[fn]就为了柔一而努力吧！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:148
translate chinese_simplified day14_2da29a08:

    # ju "「Nobody's talking about that!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 172)
    ju "「谁都没这么说过！！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:159
translate chinese_simplified day14_2a493549:

    # so "「[ln]-senpai... fight!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 184)
    so "「[ln]前辈……加油」"

# game/day 14.rpy:160
translate chinese_simplified day14_059ff5d1:

    # "Everybody's in a pretty good mood,\neven the members who are usually quiet are active.{p}This is an odd atmosphere for departing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 186-187-188)
    "总觉得大家都很兴奋啊，{w=.3} 平时很稳重的人都这么积极。{p} 这种微妙的配合，形成了出行的气氛呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:161
translate chinese_simplified day14_2e61acc1:

    # "It seems like everybody's looking forward to this.{p}We're going to be staying overnight this time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 190-191)
    "看来大家都乐在其中呢。{p} 不管怎样，这次可是要在外面留宿呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:169
translate chinese_simplified day14_ac7bcbec:

    # to "「So, what kind of punishment game is it going to be?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 201)
    to "「那，惩罚游戏干什么好？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:170
translate chinese_simplified day14_3e5b2461:

    # ka "「We might as well do something flashy.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 204)
    ka "「既然要干就干点大的吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:171
translate chinese_simplified day14_6aeb685f:

    # fn "「Oooh, that's mean...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 207)
    fn "「呜呜呜，好过分……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:180
translate chinese_simplified day14_3ee74282:

    # ta "「Hey, hey, let's not pester [fn] that much.\n If we're all here, it'll be a waste of time\n if we don't get started soon.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 218-219)
    ta "「喂喂，欺负[fn]就到此为止吧。{p} 既然都到齐了，不快点出发的话就太浪费时间了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:181
translate chinese_simplified day14_3956cacc:

    # fn "「Whew, I've been saved.{p} ...Wait.{w=.3} What are we doing with the luggage?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 222-223)
    fn "「呼～得救了。{p} ……诶？{w=.3} 行李之类的要怎么办？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:182
translate chinese_simplified day14_a2653da1:

    # ta "「I borrowed the truck from home, so it'll\n be riding in the back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 226-227)
    ta "「俺从俺家借了辆卡车出来，坐到后面去吧。{p} 昨天已经装了基本的必需品了，{w=.3}"

# game/day 14.rpy:183
translate chinese_simplified day14_31e90c0e:

    # ta "「I packed all the stuff we might need yesterday,\n so there's no problem.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 228)
    ta "没问题的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:184
translate chinese_simplified day14_82505350:

    # ky "「I looked it over to make sure Tatsuki-san\n didn't forget anything.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 231)
    ky "「我来检查下辰兄有没有漏带东西吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:188
translate chinese_simplified day14_096bd9ce:

    # ta "「You're terrible. I doubt I did.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 235)
    ta "「真过分啊。{w=.3}居然怀疑俺」"

# game/day 14.rpy:189
translate chinese_simplified day14_777b7241:

    # fn "「Ahaha, Tatsu-nii missed something, didn't he?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 238)
    fn "「啊哈哈，辰兄的话应该会漏掉什么东西吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:193
translate chinese_simplified day14_c1ca07a6:

    # so "「Um, will we be safe ridin' in the back?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 242)
    so "「那个，坐在货架上也没问题吗？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:197
translate chinese_simplified day14_2c04bdf3:

    # ta "「Gahaha! We're in the country, you'll be fine.{p} Satsuki and May also rode in the back when they\n moved.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 246-247)
    ta "「噶哈哈，{w=.3}这里是乡下啦。{w=.3}没问题的。{p} 小月和小梅也是坐在货架上搬家的嘛」"

# game/day 14.rpy:205
translate chinese_simplified day14_3fb8baf6:

    # su "「It's like the opening of that movie.{p} My Neighbor Toto...{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 257-258)
    su "「是电影的开头对吧。{p} 我的邻居龙，龙…………呃呃？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:207
translate chinese_simplified day14_40d0e810:

    # extend " mfphmfph.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 258)
    extend "我的邻居龙，龙…………呃呃？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:208
translate chinese_simplified day14_f0cad0a2:

    # ju "「Kodori, you don't need to say any more.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 261)
    ju "「古酉，接下来的就别说了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:209
translate chinese_simplified day14_b19469f1:

    # ka "「Guys usually go out into the country on their\n motorbikes without a helmet.{p} You'll be fine on the way to the campsite.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 264-265-266)
    ka "「在乡下的话，坐摩托车的大叔 不带安全帽跑来跑去什么的，都很常见呢。{p} 从这里到露营地的话，没问题的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:216
translate chinese_simplified day14_8d11ba39:

    # ta "「You don't need to think about a thing, just\n leave it to me, we don't have time to wait.{p} If you get it,{w=.3} then let's go, let's go!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 275-276-277)
    ta "「这些事就别去想了，交给俺就好啦， 时间可是不等人的。{p} 明白了就出发吧，{w=.3}上车上车」"

# game/day 14.rpy:217
translate chinese_simplified day14_e04ff328:

    # ko "「Aand we're off!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 280)
    ko "「出发～」"

# game/day 14.rpy:227
translate chinese_simplified day14_8be93eec:

    # su "「Waah, it's high up here...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 294)
    su "「呜哇，好高……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:228
translate chinese_simplified day14_8b9277fd:

    # ky "「Shun, it's dangerous to stand.{w=.3} Sit down, okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 297)
    ky "「峻，站着很危险的哦。{w=.3}快坐下来吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:235
translate chinese_simplified day14_421a5700:

    # si "「Sorry, but I'm going to take the passenger seat.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 309)
    si "「那么不好意思，我去坐副驾驶座了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:241
translate chinese_simplified day14_b6b08366:

    # "Because Shin-kun has asthma, of course getting\nin the back of the truck would be too physically\ndemanding."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 312)
    "因为深有哮喘，坐货架会挺耗费体力，所以这是理所当然的啊。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:242
translate chinese_simplified day14_2b2c8a14:

    # "Wait, Shin-kun in the back of the truck..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 313)
    "等等，坐在货架上的深……"

# game/day 14.rpy:243
translate chinese_simplified day14_7651ec37:

    # "He'd hate that. Such a low-class thing to do\ndoesn't suit Shin-kun at all.\nIf Shin-kun had something more glamorous..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 315-316)
    "不要那样，这么贫穷的臭东西和深一点都不配。{p} 深就应该更豪华一点。{p}高，高级轿车……{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:244
translate chinese_simplified day14_e23482c9:

    # "A-a limousine!{p}If he had a limousine, then we could be going\nin style!!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 317)
    "坐上高级轿车，{w=.3}风光无限地出发吧！！"

# game/day 14.rpy:248
translate chinese_simplified day14_adbeef2a:

    # ta "「Hey, [fn], what are you just standing there for?{p} Are you going to be late again?Let's leave already.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 322-323)
    ta "「喂，[fn]，傻站在那干什么。{p} 又想迟到吗？ 要丢下你了哦」"

# game/day 14.rpy:249
translate chinese_simplified day14_a0f2e9d0:

    # fn "「Oh wait, I'm getting in.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 326)
    fn "「啊啊，等下，马上就来」"

# game/day 14.rpy:250
translate chinese_simplified day14_bebcd3f0:

    # "Oops. Recently, I haven't been able \nto stop daydreaming."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 328)
    "不行不行，最近一旦开启妄想模式，就停不下来了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:257
translate chinese_simplified day14_ff5fa5ec:

    # to "「Is everybody in?{p} All right, Tatsu-nii, let's go.{p} I'm sincerely begging you, drive safely.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 340-341)
    to "「所有人都坐上来了吗？ {p} 可以了辰兄，出发吧。{p} 麻烦你尽量安全驾驶，{w=.3}开慢点仔细点小心点。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:258
translate chinese_simplified day14_32de9f05:

    # to "「Go slow and carefully, there are a lot of\n people back here...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 342)
    to "因为货架上坐了很多人呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:259
translate chinese_simplified day14_08bebe53:

    # ta "「I know, I won't drive fast.{p} You don't need to keep telling me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 345-346)
    ta "「知道了啦，不飞起来就行了吧。{p} 不说我也知道啦」"

# game/day 14.rpy:260
translate chinese_simplified day14_b1b089d8:

    # fn "「I wonder if we'll be all right if he's driving...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 349)
    fn "「没问题吧，辰兄的驾驶……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:261
translate chinese_simplified day14_ee7abbe0:

    # to "「Ah, you probably shouldn't worry.{p} He's dangerous at full speed,\n but he's not a bad driver.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 352-353)
    to "「嗯，大概不用担心了。{p} 开出能飞起来的速度虽然很危险，{w=.3}"

# game/day 14.rpy:262
translate chinese_simplified day14_aea607c5:

    # to "「He's actually pretty good.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 354)
    to "但那倒不是因为他驾驶技术差，{p}应该说是很擅长才对」"

# game/day 14.rpy:263
translate chinese_simplified day14_e5443d48:

    # fn "「He should be a racer, not a carpenter...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 357)
    fn "「那别当木工，去当赛车手不是更好……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:267
translate chinese_simplified day14_89e414ad:

    # to "「Yeah.{w=.3} If his family business was racing,\n I think he'd become a street racer.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 361-362)
    to "「就是啊。{w=.3}如果家业不一样的话，肯定会变成赛车手， 或是变成暴走族吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:268
translate chinese_simplified day14_fafb7fd1:

    # ta "「I can hear you from the driver's seat!{p} Are you always doing that on purpose?!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 365-366)
    ta "「你们，俺坐在驾驶席上可是也能听的一清二楚的！{p} 老是这样老是这样，你们是故意的吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:272
translate chinese_simplified day14_76ec6132:

    # to "「Oh, Tatsu-nii's mad!{w=.3} Run away!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 370)
    to "「啊，辰兄发火了。{w=.3}快逃！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:273
translate chinese_simplified day14_8acfc09b:

    # fn "「We can't run, we're on the back of a truck.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 373)
    fn "「怎么逃，这里是货架上啊……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:274
translate chinese_simplified day14_9536f1a9:

    # si "「It doesn't matter, are we leaving soon?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 376)
    si "「怎么都行，能不能快点出发」"

# game/day 14.rpy:278
translate chinese_simplified day14_cbab5e88:

    # "「Okay...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 380)
    "「是……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:282
translate chinese_simplified day14_c13bc5bf:

    # "From now on, we're camping.\nI wonder what's waiting for us.{p}Well, let's enjoy it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 385-386)
    "等下就要去露营了，会有什么事情等着呢。{p} 让我们拭目以待吧。"

# game/day 14.rpy:290
translate chinese_simplified day14_681c7069:

    # fn "「Wow,{w=.3} this is a nice place.{p} It's like we're really out in nature.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 394-395)
    fn "「诶，{w=.3}居然有这样的地方呢。{p} 像是纯天然形成的景色」"

# game/day 14.rpy:291
translate chinese_simplified day14_04296e86:

    # "The campground is 30 minutes away from Minasato\nVillage, there's a nice view of the area.{p}Or should I say most of the field."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 397-398-399)
    "露营的地点在距离水乡村约30分钟车程的草原。{w=.3} 草原很是宽广，景色也不错。{p} 或者更准确地说，这里基本都是原野？"

# game/day 14.rpy:292
translate chinese_simplified day14_e1b45402:

    # "It looks like there's a restroom,{w=.3} but the rest of\nplace feels like it's untouched.{p}I wonder if it's being maintained."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 401-402-403)
    "虽然似乎是有厕所之类的地方，{w=.3} 不过貌似没有什么人活动过的痕迹。{p} 是不是还在开发中呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:299
translate chinese_simplified day14_c32ebe5b:

    # ta "「Really?{w=.3} It's not that much different\n from Minasato, even though we're so far away.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 412-413)
    ta "「是吗？{w=.3} 不是和水乡村没多大区别嘛。{p} 而且又没有离开村子很远」"

# game/day 14.rpy:300
translate chinese_simplified day14_84cd3959:

    # fn "「Ehh,{w=.3} I've never seen such beautiful scenery in the\n village.{w} It's like it's become a deeper green...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 416-417)
    fn "「诶～{w=.3}不觉得景色看起来比村子里要漂亮吗。{p} 绿色更加浓厚了……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:301
translate chinese_simplified day14_b1185d30:

    # ky "「It's because the mountains are at a higher elevation\n than the village.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 420)
    ky "「因为比起在村里，我们现在更进到深山中，海拔也高了不少吧。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:302
translate chinese_simplified day14_5f7fbc08:

    # ky "「We don't really notice since we're used to this,\n but it might be different to you,\n since you've been in the city.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 421-422)
    ky "我们都看惯了所以都没什么感觉，{w=.3} 从城市回来的你可能看起来感觉不太一样吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:306
translate chinese_simplified day14_5b973214:

    # so "「But it does feel better than usual.{p} It changes when the mood is different, doesn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 426-427)
    so "「不过总觉得比平时心情更好了呢。{p} 心情也会起变化这点不是都一样嘛」"

# game/day 14.rpy:307
translate chinese_simplified day14_1a47da86:

    # ky "「Ah, that's right.{p} Besides, you grew up in the city.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 430-431)
    ky "「嗯，说的也是。{p} 而且宗也是在城市里长大的呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:308
translate chinese_simplified day14_a669e938:

    # so "「Yeah.{w} The air here is delicious.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 434)
    so "「嗯啊。{p}空气好清新～」"

# game/day 14.rpy:317
translate chinese_simplified day14_4653793e:

    # ka "「We're camping in a different spot.{p} I wonder if sleeping in a tent is any fun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 446-447)
    ka "「露营的话，比起周围的环境变了， 在帐篷里留宿这点才是最让人期待的吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:318
translate chinese_simplified day14_4b0879ad:

    # to "「Yeah, we're so far from the village\n that it doesn't matter.{p} Let's hurry up and start.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 450-451)
    to "「是啊，离村子是远是近都没关系啦。{p} 快点开始吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:322
translate chinese_simplified day14_9f0a4c6d:

    # su "「Woof,{w=.3} let's begin!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 455)
    su "「哇呼，{w=.3}开始吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:326
translate chinese_simplified day14_23a54be6:

    # su "「But is the manager not here?{p} There aren't any other people staying here either.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 459-460)
    su "「不过，这里没有管理员先生在吗？{p} 也没看见别的客人呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:330
translate chinese_simplified day14_d911df55:

    # "He's right, there's nobody else here."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 465)
    "说起来真的一个人都没有呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:331
translate chinese_simplified day14_bacf3f7e:

    # "That doesn't mean we have everything at our\ndisposal, but it's nice to have the whole\ncampground to ourselves."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 467-468)
    "虽然这里也不是什么东西都很齐全， 但明明感觉挺不错的露营地里就只有[fn]们而已。"

# game/day 14.rpy:338
translate chinese_simplified day14_07eb9f6c:

    # ka "「Minasato itself is a hard-to-reach place.{p} People like to camp in the mountains over there.{p} I don't think they come here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 477-478-479)
    ka "「因为水乡村本身就已经在偏僻的地方了。{p} 这样的村子里的深山中的露营地什么的， 基本上没人会来吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:339
translate chinese_simplified day14_d8fd9941:

    # ky "「We should be grateful for this simplicity.{p} We have water and other minimum facilities,\n and we don't have to worry about anybody around us.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 482-483-484)
    ky "「而且周围什么都没有呢。{p} 城市里的人都是去热闹的地方，{w=.3} 在设备齐全的地方露营」"

# game/day 14.rpy:340
translate chinese_simplified day14_1f670503:

    # ka "「And there's also a noisy guy.{p} Look over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 492-493)
    ka "「因为有很吵的家伙在嘛。{p} 看对面」"

# game/day 14.rpy:347
translate chinese_simplified day14_49f9377a:

    # to "「Hey hey hey,{w=.3} let's unload the luggage!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 501)
    to "「来来来，{w=.3}把行李都放下来吧！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:353
translate chinese_simplified day14_5bed97c4:

    # si "「Fu,{w=.3} I envy your abundant energy.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 508)
    si "「呼，{w=.3}真羡慕精力过剩的人呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:358
translate chinese_simplified day14_7ee257db:

    # to "「You wanna help?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 513)
    to "「要不分点给你？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:359
translate chinese_simplified day14_da04091c:

    # si "「No, I'll pass.{p} I wouldn't be able to keep up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 518-519)
    si "「不，不用了。{p} 我没办法像你们一样」"

# game/day 14.rpy:360
translate chinese_simplified day14_e2116904:

    # to "「If you're jealous,{w=.3} don't be so reserved.{p} It's unexpected of you to say something nice to me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 522-523)
    to "「别客气啦，{w=.3}不是很羡慕嘛。{p} 深居然会夸奖我还真是意外呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:365
translate chinese_simplified day14_0d3a778b:

    # ju "「I don't think it would be praise if he wasn't\n being reserved...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 529)
    ju "「我觉得他既没有客气，也没有夸你……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:369
translate chinese_simplified day14_aacf4fd0:

    # si "「Wouldn't there be nothing to worry about if those\n muscles were in your head?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 534-535)
    si "「脑袋中也充满肌肉的话， 就应该不会有烦恼吧？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:373
translate chinese_simplified day14_e0be0835:

    # to "「Y-{w=.3}you don't need to go that far...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 539)
    to "「没，{w=.3}没必要说到这种程度吧……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:374
translate chinese_simplified day14_17cd4cfe:

    # ju "「Tora... Kuroi doesn't mean any harm.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 542)
    ju "「虎……黑井没有恶意的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:378
translate chinese_simplified day14_1df2c8e2:

    # ju "「It is a very rare occurrence,{w=.3}\n but this is a good time for you to be a noisy guy.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 546-547)
    ju "「虽然这种情况比较少，{w=.3} 但有时候有些吵闹的家伙在反而更好呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:382
translate chinese_simplified day14_d1e38398:

    # to "「Juuichi-senpai!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 551)
    to "「柔一前辈」"

# game/day 14.rpy:386
translate chinese_simplified day14_cf75a784:

    # ju "「Don't hug me, get off.{p} Hey, don't rub my belly!{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 555-556)
    ju "「别抱过来，离远点。{p} 喂，不要揉我的肚子！{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:389
translate chinese_simplified day14_19d56e52:

    # extend "...Tora,{w=.3} it seems like you want me to be angry!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 557)
    extend "……虎，{w=.3}看来你是很想惹我生气是吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:390
translate chinese_simplified day14_25e8c8fd:

    # ju "「Humph!」{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 560)
    ju "「哼！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:395
translate chinese_simplified day14_f9c8d755:

    # extend "{w=.3}"
    extend ""

# game/day 14.rpy:403
translate chinese_simplified day14_7e34d5b7:

    # fn "「Why won't Torahiko stay quiet if he knows he's\n going to get thrown...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 569-570)
    fn "「为什么虎彦明知会被扔出去， 还是不肯安分下来呢……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:404
translate chinese_simplified day14_30eba895:

    # ky "「Who knows.{w=.3} Maybe he doesn't think about it if\n he doesn't know...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 573)
    ky "「谁知道呢。{w=.3}可能是什么都没去想吧……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:405
translate chinese_simplified day14_525485b8:

    # ta "「All right,{w=.3} leave the guy doing the control\n alone and I'll assign roles.{p} Let's get this set up before sunset.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 576-577-578)
    ta "「好了，{w=.3}在演闹剧的家伙就别管了， 分配下任务，快点行动吧。{p} 不快点的话太阳要下山咯」"

# game/day 14.rpy:406
translate chinese_simplified day14_53ddbcce:

    # fn "「Something like a cooking team,{w=.3} a campfire team,{w=.3}\n and a tent team?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 581-582)
    fn "「料理，{w=.3}篝火，{w=.3}还有帐篷。{p} 这三组是吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:407
translate chinese_simplified day14_eae0dd04:

    # ta "「I'll put up the tent.{p} This thing is mine.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 585)
    ta "「俺去建帐篷吧。{p}这可是俺出场的时候」"

# game/day 14.rpy:408
translate chinese_simplified day14_cd19a485:

    # fn "「Cooking is something that never did suit you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 588)
    fn "「因为辰兄不适合料理什么的嘛」"

# game/day 14.rpy:412
translate chinese_simplified day14_dfd805bb:

    # ta "「Well,{w=.3} I can make stuff like drinking snacks,\n so I can do a little.{p} I'm pretty good at it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 592-593-594)
    ta "「俺说啊。{w=.3}下酒菜什么的都是俺自己做的啦， 一点点的话俺还是会的。{p} 因为俺很能干嘛」"

# game/day 14.rpy:416
translate chinese_simplified day14_24f9707f:

    # to "「All right then,{w=.3} I'll take control of the cooking\n team, even though I already decided that from \n the beginning.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 599-600-601)
    to "「痛痛痛，{w=.3}那我去负责料理吧。{p} 不过这也是早就定好了的。{p} 材料也都带过来了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:417
translate chinese_simplified day14_b5ebd21d:

    # to "「I brought the ingredients, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 601)
    to "材料也都带过来了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:418
translate chinese_simplified day14_54467fd2:

    # ky "「Should I prepare the campfire?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 604)
    ky "「那我就去准备一下篝火吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:425
translate chinese_simplified day14_cea7a55c:

    # ka "「We need to get firewood.{p} Should I do that?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 612-613)
    ka "「只要捡柴薪就行了吧。{p} 那我也弄这个吧……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:429
translate chinese_simplified day14_ac4cfbd7:

    # su "「I'll help too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 617)
    su "「我也来帮忙」"

# game/day 14.rpy:437
translate chinese_simplified day14_9cbb526f:

    # ta "「Hey, handyman,{w=.3} help me out here.{p} You work with this kind of stuff.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 626-627)
    ta "「喂，万事屋，{w=.3}过来帮忙啊。{p} 这种事也办得到吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:441
translate chinese_simplified day14_ddfd000e:

    # ko "「My house is a hardware store, not a general store,\n we do things like machine repair and replacement.{w=.3}\n I've never touched a tent.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 631-632-633)
    ko "「我家不是什么万事屋，是五金行啊。{p} 确实有做过机器修理什么的，{w=.3} 不过帐篷碰都没碰过啊」"

# game/day 14.rpy:442
translate chinese_simplified day14_e60de771:

    # ta "「You've never done this?{p} If that's the case, I'll have to try to teach you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 636-637)
    ta "「没干过？ 那俺教你，来试试吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:443
translate chinese_simplified day14_039d4f6d:

    # ko "「Oh,{w=.3} all right then...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 640)
    ko "「啊，嗯。{w=.3}那样的话……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:447
translate chinese_simplified day14_24259d64:

    # "Somehow I didn't get assigned a role.{p}I wonder what I should try."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 645)
    "看来大家都分好组了。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:456
translate chinese_simplified day14_7b25ade6:

    # ko "「Aah, I'm tired.{p} And really hungry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 656-657)
    ko "「啊～～累了。{p} 肚子已经饿得咕咕叫了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:460
translate chinese_simplified day14_17006094:

    # ta "「What?{w=.3} Aren't you always hungry?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 661)
    ta "「什么嘛，{w=.3}你不是一直都肚子饿的么」"

# game/day 14.rpy:468
translate chinese_simplified day14_7b936c55:

    # ky "「That took longer than I expected.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 671)
    ky "「比想象中要花时间呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:469
translate chinese_simplified day14_69951cad:

    # ka "「I didn't expect it to be that tough to gather\n firewood...{p} Are you all right, Shun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 674-675)
    ka "「想不到捡柴薪会这么累……{p} 峻没问题吧？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:473
translate chinese_simplified day14_df74ee1d:

    # su "「We survived since Kouya-san brought so much.{p} Thank you very much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 679-680)
    su "「洸哉哥帮我拿了很多，所以没那么累啦。{p} 谢谢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:474
translate chinese_simplified day14_09e36cac:

    # ka "「It's nothing... I just got as much as I could.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 683)
    ka "「没事……我只是拿自己能拿得动的量而已」"

# game/day 14.rpy:484
translate chinese_simplified day14_62059568:

    # to "「All right then,{w=.3} the curry is done.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 694)
    to "「久等了～{w=.3}咖喱做好了哦」"

# game/day 14.rpy:491
translate chinese_simplified day14_908b7ffe:

    # ko "「Wow, it looks delicious.{w} You made all this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 702-703)
    ko "「哇～看上去很好吃呢。{p}这些全部都是虎彦做的吗？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:492
translate chinese_simplified day14_eaa911a3:

    # to "「Well,{w=.3} I had a few helpers.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 705)
    to "「嗯，{w=.3}在他们帮忙下做出来的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:493
translate chinese_simplified day14_8bee45b9:

    # so "「I helped out too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 708)
    so "「我也帮忙了哦！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:497
translate chinese_simplified day14_3bd0bfd9:

    # si "「I don't know what everybody's tastes are,\n but I think this should be good enough.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 713-714)
    si "「虽然不知道合不合大家口味， 应该做得还可以的」"

# game/day 14.rpy:498
translate chinese_simplified day14_838589e6:

    # "The cooking team is a surprising combination.{p}It's a mix of those who cook and one who doesn't.{p}It just happened to be their hobby."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 716-717-718)
    "料理组真是些意外的成员呢，{w=.3} 好像和料理完全没关系的人都混在里面了。{p} 可能是觉得有兴趣才干的。"

# game/day 14.rpy:499
translate chinese_simplified day14_f9441417:

    # to "「Anyway, let's try it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 721)
    to "「总之，先吃吃看吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:508
translate chinese_simplified day14_ec263634:

    # ky "「Let's sit down, everybody.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 732)
    ky "「那大家都坐到座位上吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:509
translate chinese_simplified day14_e8b47e31:

    # "Hmm, I wonder what this will taste like."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 734)
    "好了，看看味道到底怎样呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:510
translate chinese_simplified day14_b2ea09be:

    # ka "「...This is pretty good.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 737)
    ka "「……好吃」"

# game/day 14.rpy:511
translate chinese_simplified day14_cd72ef01:

    # ta "「It's sweet but it tastes good.{w=.3} It's rich.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 740)
    ta "「虽然是甜的，但还是挺好吃的呢。{w=.3}而且味道还很浓郁」"

# game/day 14.rpy:512
translate chinese_simplified day14_d2a31115:

    # su "「It's delicious!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 743)
    su "「很好吃啊～」"

# game/day 14.rpy:513
translate chinese_simplified day14_66295d4e:

    # ky "「There's a good depth of flavor...{w=.3}\n What did you put in it?{p} It's a little sweet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 746-747)
    ky "「味道很浓厚，所以很好吃呢。{w=.3}……放了什么进去呢？{p} 有点太甜了点」"

# game/day 14.rpy:520
translate chinese_simplified day14_79571157:

    # to "「Heh heh heh.{p} We had a bit of trouble,{w=.3} Juuichi-senpai\n just happened to bring his honey and he put in a lot.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 756-757-758)
    to "「嘿嘿嘿。{p}发生了一点意外，{w=.3} 柔一前辈拿的蜂蜜， 不小心往咖喱里放太多了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:524
translate chinese_simplified day14_10177e8b:

    # to "「Right,{w=.3} Senpai?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 762)
    to "「呐，{w=.3}前辈？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:528
translate chinese_simplified day14_8dd6ac20:

    # ju "「Tora,{w=.3} that's enough of you!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 766)
    ju "「虎，{w=.3}你这家伙给我适可而止！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:529
translate chinese_simplified day14_57603415:

    # su "「Juuichi-san's face is bright red.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 769)
    su "「柔一哥满脸通红了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:530
translate chinese_simplified day14_2c349a3a:

    # ju "「Prepare yourself!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 772)
    ju "「觉悟吧！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:531
translate chinese_simplified day14_814b79aa:

    # to "「Hehe,{w=.3} this place is so spacious that\n I've got plenty of room to run away.」{w} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 775)
    to "「嘿嘿，{w=.3}周围这么宽敞，怎么逃都可以呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:534
translate chinese_simplified day14_3d1a9ff7:

    # extend "{w=.01}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 781)
    extend "虎彦敏捷地闪开想要抓住他的柔一，"

# game/day 14.rpy:536
translate chinese_simplified day14_8575df97:

    # extend "{w=.1}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 784)
    extend "柔一也丝毫不放过立马追了上去。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:539
translate chinese_simplified day14_39f4e17d:

    # extend "{w=.25}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 785)
    extend "应该是虎彦的脚速快一点吧。"

# game/day 14.rpy:543
translate chinese_simplified day14_6297dff7:

    # "Juuichi-san tries to grab Torahiko, but he\nnimbly dodges and runs away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 781-782-783)
    "虎彦敏捷地闪开想要抓住他的柔一， 并且迅速跑了出去。"

# game/day 14.rpy:544
translate chinese_simplified day14_e2b827d6:

    # "Juuichi-san chases after him.{p}I guess Torahiko is quicker on his feet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 784-785)
    "柔一也丝毫不放过立马追了上去。{p} 应该是虎彦的脚速快一点吧。"

# game/day 14.rpy:554
translate chinese_simplified day14_aeb11281:

    # si "「Can't they be quiet while we're eating?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 796)
    si "「吃饭的时候就不能安静点吗？」"

# game/day 14.rpy:555
translate chinese_simplified day14_4d324588:

    # ky "「It looks like he knew he was going to be thrown\n this time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 799)
    ky "「这次应该是知道会被扔出去才这样做的吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:556
translate chinese_simplified day14_252703e8:

    # su "「They look like they're having fun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 802)
    su "「看上去很高兴呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:557
translate chinese_simplified day14_36664ef4:

    # ka "「This is what usually happens when we eat...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 805)
    ka "「我们只要照常吃饭就好了……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:558
translate chinese_simplified day14_b5f64dfc:

    # "I'm somewhat getting used to seeing this.{p}Still, this is nice.{p}Just as I thought,{w=.3} curry tastes delicious outdoors."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 807-808-809)
    "不知道为什么，[fn]也开始看惯这样的场景了呢……{p} 那也有那样的好处吧，{w=.3}嗯。{p} 果然，在大自然中品尝咖喱的话，感觉特别美味呢。"

# game/day 14.rpy:565
translate chinese_simplified day14_92fa1391:

    # ju "「I won't forgive you today!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 818)
    ju "「今天绝对不会放过你的！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:566
translate chinese_simplified day14_d3d6aa09:

    # to "「Heh!{w=.3} Catch me, catch me if you can!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 821)
    to "「嘿，{w=.3}要是抓得住的话就来抓抓看看啊！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:577
translate chinese_simplified day14_5d5a4e09:

    # ka "「Why are we also having curry for dinner?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 835)
    ka "「为什么晚饭又是咖喱啊」"

# game/day 14.rpy:578
translate chinese_simplified day14_5a40e76a:

    # to "「You eat curry when you go camping.{p} There's still some left.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 838-839)
    to "「要说露营的话当然是咖喱了啊。{p} 还有很多哦」"

# game/day 14.rpy:579
translate chinese_simplified day14_2f810eeb:

    # ka "「Don't tell me we're eating curry tomorrow too...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 842)
    ka "「难不成明天也是吃咖喱吗……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:583
translate chinese_simplified day14_3c6eaa9b:

    # to "「You don't know?{p} Curry tastes even better when it sits overnight.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 846-847)
    to "「你不知道么？{p} 咖喱要放一晚才好吃呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:587
translate chinese_simplified day14_1e5f87ff:

    # ka "「I'm going to kill you...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 851)
    ka "「杀了你……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:592
translate chinese_simplified day14_0f7e2f14:

    # ta "「Well,{w=.3} I already ate everything up.{p} I'm eating to charge myself up for later.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 858-859)
    ta "「算啦，这不是也挺好吗，{w=.3}反正都已经吃过了。{p} 肚子也已经填饱了，等下还有事要干呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:593
translate chinese_simplified day14_618bce59:

    # fn "「That's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 862)
    fn "「说的也是」"

# game/day 14.rpy:597
translate chinese_simplified day14_7e498bdf:

    # fn "「Then let's start the campfire.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 869)
    fn "「那，现在开始篝火晚会吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:598
translate chinese_simplified day14_7131a27c:

    # "I light the prepared firewood."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 873)
    "因为已经按易燃的形状搭建好了，{w=.3}"

# game/day 14.rpy:599
translate chinese_simplified day14_e79b1c18:

    # "Since it was set up so that it'll easily burn,{w=.3}\nthe small flame grows into a great fire in the\nblink of an eye."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 874-875)
    "小小的火花转眼间就变成熊熊燃烧的火焰。{p} 开心的晚会要开始了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:600
translate chinese_simplified day14_20cc904f:

    # "The lively party begins."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 875)
    "开心的晚会要开始了。"

# game/day 14.rpy:606
translate chinese_simplified day14_28f02095:

    # ky "「Today went by so quickly.{p} It got dark before we were able to do anything.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 883-884)
    ky "「总觉得今天过得真快呀。{p} 什么都没干就已经天黑了」"

# game/day 14.rpy:607
translate chinese_simplified day14_9321a1c2:

    # so "「You're right.{p} But the day still hasn't ended yet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 887-888)
    so "「就是呀。{p} 不过今天还不算结束哦，现在才是开始呢」"

# game/day 14.rpy:615
translate chinese_simplified day14_9d38c434:

    # ta "「Yep, it's going to be night.{p} Well, let's start off with a toast.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 898-899)
    ta "「就是，夜晚现在才刚刚开始呢。{p} 嘛，首先先来干杯吧」"

# game/day 14.rpy:616
translate chinese_simplified day14_5d625350:

    # fn "「...Tatsu-nii,{w=.3} did you bring alcohol?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 902)
    fn "「……辰兄，{w=.3}你带酒来了吗？"

# game/day 14.rpy:617
translate chinese_simplified day14_568ee5a1:

    # ta "「Isn't that natural?{w=.3} Of course I'm going to\n drink when I'm here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 905-906)
    ta "「当然啦，{w=.3}现在不喝等什么时候喝啊。{p} 用河水冰过了之后很凉哦。{p}"

# game/day 14.rpy:618
translate chinese_simplified day14_6ce9dfa1:

    # ta "「I let it chill in the river water.{p} Bwah- it's delicious!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 907)
    ta "噗啊～～好喝！」"

# game/day 14.rpy:619
translate chinese_simplified day14_8dcf45f8:

    # ju "「Tatsu-san, are you sure that's all right?{p} You should restrain yourself, since we're in the\n mountains...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 14日目.ks (KS 910-911)
    ju "「辰，不会有问题吧？{p} 既然在深山里就应该多少控制点……」"

# game/day 14.rpy:620
translate chinese_simplified day14_71c881e0:

